<plot>New Orleans filmmakers follow a child victim of Hurricane Katrina as she relives the events of the hurricane and its aftermath. In this short documentary film, Kaylen, a twelve year old girl, writes President Bush as she speaks of her destroyed home, her lost friends, and her uncertain fate. Come with Kaylen on her personal journey. See and hear the major players of Hurricane Katrina and draw your own conclusion as to Kaylen's fate.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?133725</url></doc>
